body.section:
Exists an implementation for the TabbedContentManagerUI and for the DesktopContentManagerUI.
To obtain a specific instance use the following (for example):
import org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content.desktop; ... contentManager.setContentManagerUI(new MyDoggyDesktopContentManagerUI());
or import org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content.tabbed; ... contentManager.setContentManagerUI(new MyDoggyTabbedContentManagerUI());
If you want to implement your own ContentManageUI, your class must implement non only the ContentManageUI interface but also the BackContentManagerUI interface in the package org.noos.xing.mydoggy.plaf.ui.content.
This is to provide all neccesary methods to use the manager.
